once upon a time in a forest, There lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree which was on the banks of a river.
in the same river, There lived a crocodile and his wife...
monkey wanted to make a clothe for himself using crocodiles skin so he slowly tired to become frients withe the crocodile
by feeding him the berrys. The berry were delicious and the crocodile liked it. after sometime, the monkey started poissening the berrys